{"id": "test-01765", "text": "- One barge, week of December 15, lower Ohio bid 2-1/2 points higher at 105 percent, no offer.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 40, "end": 44, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Ohio"}]}
{"id": "test-01766", "text": "Two barges, week of January 5, Illinois, offered five points lower at 195 percent, bid at 150 percent.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 31, "end": 39, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Illinois"}]}
{"id": "test-01767", "text": "- Five barges, 30-day open, mid-Mississippi (McGregor and south) bid at 160 percent, offered at 170 percent, no comparisons.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 28, "end": 43, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "mid-Mississippi"}, {"start": 45, "end": 53, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "McGregor"}]}
